{"tid":1222902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海外戰線】是咁的，我地整咗多國語言嘅612懶人包","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:28:38.000Z","uid":239995,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1010884be667040f4ce077a7c93f2e0c124284f2","tid":1222902,"uid":239995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>【煩請廣傳】</strong><br />\n讓香港612給世界看見！<br />\n6月16 - 17日（星期日及一），是香港另一個關鍵時刻。<br />\n我和朋友，正準備一些翻譯成各國語言的「懶人包」，<br />\n想要精要地告訴世界，香港發生了什麼事。<br />\n這幾天，我們看到外國的回應，各方同路人的努力，局勢開始變了。<br />\n在走上街頭之外，我們每個人都可發揮自己的力量，去把戰線擴大至全世界。<br />\n我們深信，輿論和故事，是有力量的！<br />\n<br />\n目前，韓文、英文、法文、台腔、日文、中文，都在整裝待發了；<br />\n還有 荷蘭、瑞典芬蘭、瑞士等在籌備中。<br />\n<br />\n我在此呼籲各方好友和專業人士：<br />\n如果你有可靠的朋友，懂其他國家的翻譯；<br />\n如果你有朋友認識各國各地各種媒體／散佈渠道／KOL；<br />\n請與我們聯絡，或者盡可能地把香港的情況散播開去。<br />\n促請各地監察及懲罰濫權、破壞民主憲制的邪惡政權。<br />\n<br />\n讓我們發揮文宣的力量，撼動世界，寫下歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我們的聯絡電郵</strong>：<strong>hk612toglobe@gmail.com</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個係中文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0Ao98K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0Ao98K.jpg&h=22669e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmJieAq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmJieAq.jpg&h=ca0a0ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUZhu8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUZhu8L.jpg&h=7647a4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15J2Gfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15J2Gfr.jpg&h=6e099070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFcyNVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFcyNVs.jpg&h=3f107da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGTNSm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGTNSm7.jpg&h=e180e072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jDxfgOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDxfgOO.jpg&h=2eeab2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2mS3tP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2mS3tP.jpg&h=91357bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TNZJtP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TNZJtP.jpg&h=fd2bf105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懶人包在此：</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1JHJyjwWDG5KgkkCRFnCkUJpQfNKUbSqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1JHJyjwWDG5KgkkCRFnCkUJpQfNKUbSqA&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=e640eb1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1JHJyjwWDG5KgkkCRFnCkUJpQfNKUbSqA</a><br />\n<br />\n目前我地已經搞掂咗以下嘅語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而呢個list係會隨時update架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHQTNXP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHQTNXP.jpg&h=5758fffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，我地唔係全能，可能有啲譯法唔係幾Native，不過而家最優先嘅係俾世界各地嘅朋友，最簡單咁睇到香港發生緊咩事。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>你可以：<br />\n1. 幫手share俾香港/外國嘅朋友仔<br />\n2. 幫我地睇下有無咩譯法係可以改善<br />\n3. 加入我地，一齊翻譯<br />\n4. 幫手收集外國討論區嘅post，等香港人知道，我地並唔孤單！</strong><br />\n<br />\n#香港憲法保衛戰"},{"pid":"3afe9987f46db46e550b6468e1185db3cebb9e44","tid":1222902,"uid":103012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c035de8299645439e2d211b318fa9ccceda308","tid":1222902,"uid":194785,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"日本啲朋友仲緊張香港過啲廢物港豬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌，一個朋友都無出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底發生咩事，無講笑"},{"pid":"0bc16210ce874b028c4a5959c99a44bcc77f0f44","tid":1222902,"uid":144354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:50:47.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"156fa8c6dd7f11ae24342009ea0fde325f98568c","tid":1222902,"uid":110177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5291206b3b27eec4d41c5a6e1297ca47d4ece31a","tid":1222902,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27621605ab70f27e78dcb0d41a71fc9cd3208fba","tid":1222902,"uid":39372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cfebf2b862b88714673b17d5d339c27d8c007b","tid":1222902,"uid":1982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f3ad440d55